flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: New or updated ASN / inbound shipment record for battery components from SAP S/4HANA (or supplier portal) indicating expected receipt within the next 72 hours.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest ASNs, POs, inventory and staging metadata from SAP S/4HANA and supplier feeds.]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Clean, enrich and transform inbound and on-hand data into planning subject areas and kitting candidates.]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Agent Team - Agentic assessment combines arrival ETAs, QC risk, and line schedule to generate kitting batches and delivery time windows.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions - Execute picks/kitting and queue inspections; write pick lists and kit reservations back to WES/SAP.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: CWB Lifecycle - Surface recommended kitting plan and any exceptions for planner approval; allow override or accept.]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Process Builder - Notify warehouse floor and line feeders; monitor execution and update subject areas with actual kit deliveries.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Timely delivery of kits to lines with minimized idle time and excess buffer, fewer stockouts, lower handling costs (reduced COGS through optimized staging/kitting), faster quarantine resolution for failed inspections, and improved OTIF for battery production.]
  N3 -->|Inbound inspection fails or lot flagg...| B1[Agent Team routes material to quarantine, triggers CWB Lifecycle exception for supplier disposition and generates return/rework instructions via Remote Functions.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Failed lots isolated, rework or supplier claim initiated, kits adjusted to use alternate lots to maintain line feed where possible.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|ASN / carrier ETA delayed beyond thre...| B2[Agent Team recalculates feed schedule, prioritizes critical kits using available inventory, and triggers reschedule notifications to carriers/WES; if shortage persists, open CWB for expedited procurement or line decoupling.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Reduced risk of line stoppage via prioritized allocation and expedited actions; planners notified for contingency execution.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Inventory or lot-level discrepancy be...| B3[STREAMS flags data quality exception and Process Builder launches reconciliation Remote Function plus CWB Lifecycle task for warehouse verification.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Discrepancy resolved or quarantined; kitting plan adjusted to reflect corrected availability, preserving traceability.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]